USAGE OF ACTIVITY IN ANDROID

TO START A ACTIVITY：they are defined in Activity.java

startActivity（Intent intent）
startActivityForResult（Intent i，int requestCode）（setResult、onActivityResult）

TO START A SERVICE：they are defined in Context.java

startService（Intent intent）
bindService(Intent intent, ServiceConnection, BIND_AUTO_CREATE);

TO SEND A BROADCAST：it is defined in Context.java

sendBroadcast（Intent intent）

TO DEFINE A PENDINGINTENT：they are definec in context

getActivity
geyService
getBroadcastReceiver

they are in the status of pending and will not be done instantly. After using the sending method it will be activated at once.

